{"tid":684368,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"月入十萬都買唔到樓","createTime":"2018-05-30T13:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T13:52:07.000Z","uid":2556,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0bc782884fcbe605d1be6545e54b14ed22af90","tid":684368,"uid":2556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:00:51.000Z","msg":"個案主角：傅太，35歲，任職公務員，月入3萬元。丈夫同為35歲，屬自僱人士，月入約7萬元。他們有兩個女兒，分別3歲和5歲。他們擁有170萬元現金，扣除家庭開支，每月可儲蓄2.5萬元。現時一家四口加傭人和公公居住，該單位由公公持有。<br />\n<br />\n理財目標：傅生一直覺得樓價貴，所以等待多年也未入市，想知道如果現在想買樓，可以怎樣計劃呢？他們心儀沙田及馬鞍山區（大圍也可以），因為怕負擔不起三房單位的首期支出，故置業目標為400平方呎左右的兩房單位，樓價600萬元以下，希望可付兩成首期。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/210009_fef209cde6867a86eddd8152decb4c8b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F210009_fef209cde6867a86eddd8152decb4c8b.png&h=663ae8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十皮都話買唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6624e073467787a8e2ed2ca221e628052a20cf","tid":684368,"uid":44854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"個人開支、家庭開支同女兒興趣班呢d大洗姐，根本唔洗用咁多<br />\n冇咁大個頭唔好帶咁大頂帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9270e14588ef037d84f773f287cbef1af8cdb9b0","tid":684368,"uid":23469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"用咩電話上網 要1500一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c7267c0c7bb359ebf989232f990593b458db2b","tid":684368,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"首先個人支出同女兒興趣班個到有d離譜，另外每個月有2萬已夠供樓，結論廢文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae8f0c115ec53d266ce9f33531ef6a963d73883","tid":68436